{"text_id":62272,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," comprehensive"," study"," of"," transient"," X","-","ray"," emission"," from"," normal"," galactic"," nuclei","."," Our"," research"," aims"," to"," address"," the"," long","-","standing"," issue"," of"," unexplained"," X","-","ray"," variability"," in"," quies","cent"," galactic"," centers",","," which"," hinders"," our"," understanding"," of"," super","massive"," black"," hole"," activity"," and"," the"," accretion"," process","."," We"," utilize"," a"," concerted"," effort"," of"," observational"," and"," theoretical"," approaches"," to"," investigate"," the"," origin"," of"," transient"," X","-","ray"," emission"," in"," a"," sample"," of"," nearby"," galaxies","."," Our"," analysis"," reveals"," a"," prevalence"," of"," transient"," X","-","ray"," events",","," characterized"," by"," rapid"," flux"," increases"," and"," decays",","," in"," galaxies"," hosting"," low","-","level"," active"," galactic"," nuclei"," (","AG","N",")"," activity","."," We"," propose"," that"," these"," transients"," are"," indicative"," of"," accretion"," disk"," inst","abilities",","," triggered"," by"," the"," disruption"," of"," stellar"," debris"," or"," the"," capture"," of"," compact"," objects"," by"," the"," central"," super","massive"," black"," hole","."," Our"," results"," provide"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," mechanisms"," governing"," the"," growth"," and"," feeding"," of"," super","massive"," black"," holes",","," offering"," a"," unique"," probe"," of"," the"," complex"," interplay"," between"," the"," central"," engine"," and"," its"," surroundings","."," This"," work"," contributes"," significantly"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," complex"," X","-","ray"," phenomena"," in"," normal"," galactic"," nuclei",","," bridging"," the"," gap"," between"," theory"," and"," observations","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}